metadata.name: Through your eyes
metadata.description:
This artwork is about the emotion of past and present of a persona. The contrast between two emotions and yet both have a similarity which is strength in a human individual. Giving space for a little vulnerability to reflect upon the self and yet have faith in growing to better places.  Looking back and moving on means to grow and bloom. Sometimes human relate to what they able to see and their perspective changes over the time. 


So, Which side are you currently relate to?
